description:
A basic 101 dental reference.

Written by a dentist.

Not useful for doctors or students of Dentistry.

Covers following topics:

Introduction to the dentistry,
Tooth anatomy,
Adult Teeth types and positions,
Child Teeth types and positions,
Tooth Structure and directions,
Tooth development and eruption,
Wisdom tooth,
Tooth diseases (Gum),
Tooth diseases (Cavities),
Disease prevention,
Tooth extraction,
Tooth Implants,
Type of Implants,
Braces.


Also added search based on customer feedback.


Please write to us. We would love to improve this app.
